title: Johara® Broad Spectrum Sunscreen SPF-30
description:
Product details of Johara® Broad Spectrum Sunscreen SPF-30

  • • Broad spectrum sunscreen Lotion
  • • Protects from both UVA and UVB rays
  • • Enriched with actives which protects from pollution
  • • May delay the signs of aging
  • • Lightens skin tone
  • • Nourishes and smoothen the skin
  • • Helps diminish pigmentation spots
  • • Keeps skin soft and supple

Sunscreen SPF 30 is a broad spectrum sunscreen that protects against UVA and UVB rays and has a protection of SPF 30. It protects the skin from harmful sunrays, prevents sun damage, including brown spots, skin discoloration and pollution. The light fragrance and silky texture make it easy to use. It is fortified with Galanga Extract, Pollution Defense Complex, Vitamin E along with sunscreen agent to provide perfect protection from sunlight and pollution along with nourishment to skin. Thus, delays the signs of aging and reduces pigmentation.

Apply Sunscreen SPF 30 onto cleansed, moisturized face and neck daily in the morning before sun exposure. It is advisable to apply 20 to 30 minutes before direct sun exposure. Re-apply every few hours or as needed.
